    dc:title "A new species of hill stream loach (Teleostei: Balitoridae) from Central Kalimantan, with redescriptions of Homaloptera tateregani Popta and Homaloptera stephensoni Hora" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189225>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189220>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189226>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189221> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189225>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Schematised drawings of anterior dorso-lateral body scales of: A, Homaloptera batek, ZRC 51743, 97.2 mm SL; B, H. tateregani, RMNH 7632, 63.2 mm SL; C, H. stephensoni, ZRC 51742, 68.6 mm SL (scale bar = 1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/189225/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189220>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Homaloptera batek, freshly caught, in push net with other syntopic species (taken at night, 12 August 2007)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/189220/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189226>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Map of Borneo showing distribution of Homaloptera batek (circle), H. tateregani (triangle) and H. stephensoni (square – solid: type locality, hollow: other locations)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/189226/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189221>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Type locality, Sungei Baha’e, Katingan basin, Central Kalimantan (13 August 2007)." ;
